About Key Skills for Reading: Vocabulary Development (School Edition)
Support your students' reading efforts with activities that build their word recognition and word analysis skills. Your students will read with greater confidence as they:

# Classify words by purpose and part of speech
# Build knowledge of essential words
# Recognize usage differences in homophones
# Construct compound words
# Build words using prefixes and suffixes
